%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">∶</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">指日可待。到时候，每</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">位上班者就要养</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">位退休者，能养得起吗？据劳动与社会保障部宣布，到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2004</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%","title":"我看社会保障制度改革","time":1233775748999}